title: Pirates of the Caribbean Soundtrack Treasures Collection
description:
Pirates of the Caribbean Soundtrack Treasures Collection
The fourth disc only without the remixes.
It contains;

1 - Pirates, Day One, 4:56
2 - Marry Me
3 - The Heart Of Davy Jones
4 - Lord Cutler Beckett
5 - Jack's Theme Bare Bones Demo
6 - Hoist The Colours Suite
7 - The Pirate Lord Of Singapore
8 - Just Good Business

And

Jo, Ho! (A Pirate's Life For Me!)


Enjoy!
